('700', 'REC', '002969', 'GRD', 'Foundations of Knowledge in Leisure Studies', 'An examination of the different paradigmatic perspective that influence the multidisciplinary field of Leisure Studies.  The interrelationships among paradigms, theories, epistemologies, and methodologies are explored, with particular attention to their application to current research in the field.  Graded on a Cr/NCr basis.', NULL, 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
