('785', 'SOC', '003065', 'GRD', 'Urban Security Governance', 'An examination of the urban aspects of security, surveillance, war and terrorism. Particular attention will be given to the contemporary embrace of resilience as a rationality of urban security. Additional themes include the militarization of policing, the role of ''big data'' in the intensification of urban surveillance, and the relationship between security and urban environments.', NULL, 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
