('412', 'GENE', '005811', 'UG', 'Ethics and the Engineering Profession', 'An analysis from the standpoint of philosophical ethics of moral issues arising in professional engineering practice. Issues include the social responsibility of engineers, conflict of interest and obligation, morally acceptable levels of risk, and moral implications of technology.', 'Prereq: Level at least 2A Engineering students.', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
