('322', 'MUSIC', '007038', 'UG', 'Conducting 2', 'A continuation of the study of conducting techniques begun in MUSIC 222. The course focuses on the development of analytical and musical skills including score study, aural skills, and gestural clarity.', 'Prereq: MUSIC 222', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
