('205', 'SOC', '008581', 'UG', 'Social Problems', 'The specific social problems discussed will vary but will include problems of well-being, problems of inequality and power, and problems related to modernization. [Note: Formerly SOC 102.]', 'Prereq: SOC 101/101R or 120R. Antireq: SOC 102', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
('200', 'SOC', '008583', 'UG', 'Sociology of Marriage and Family', 'An introduction to the sociological perspectives on marriage and the family in urban-industrial societies. Special attention is given to marriage and the family in Canada. Comparisons with U.S. and Britain will be undertaken.', 'Prereq: SOC 101/101R or 120R', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
('201', 'SOC', '008584', 'UG', 'Victims and Society', 'This course will examine the substance of victimization: the scientific study of victims, the process, etiology, and consequences of victimization. Topics will include victims and politics, the victims'' movement, victim-precipitation, the victimization of women, and family violence.', 'Prereq: SOC 101/101R or 120R', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
