('227', 'SOC', '008609', 'UG', 'Criminology', 'An examination of the major theories of crime causation and their implications for the development of social policy. Both historical and contemporary theories will be discussed.', 'Prereq: SOC 101/101R or 120R', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
