('228', 'SOC', '008610', 'UG', 'Sociology of Criminal Justice', 'Decisions to process offenders and the role of social factors in the Canadian criminal justice system are critically examined. Focal issues include police discretion, the legal profession, and prison systems.', 'Prereq: SOC 101/101R or 120R', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
