('222R', 'SOCWK', '008751', 'UG', 'Community Organization', 'An examination of social work practice as it relates to functional and geographical communities. The course will explore the theoretical foundations of organization practice as well as a variety of models. [Note: SWREN 222R is available only to students who have been given conditional admission to the BSW program; such students must have already completed their first undergraduate degree.]', 'Prereq: SOCWK 120R', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
