('355R', 'SOCWK', '008767', 'UG', 'Child Maltreatment: Identification and Prevention', 'The objectives of this course are to provide an understanding of the dimensions and causes of child maltreatment, to develop skills identifying cases of this social problem, and to explore current methods of management and treatment of persons involved in child maltreatment situations.', 'Prereq: SOCWK 120R', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
