('220R', 'EASIA', '011391', 'UG', 'The History of East Asian Communities in Canada', 'This course examines the evolution of the Chinese, Japanese, and Korean communities in Canada as well as their significance for Canadian economic, social, and political life in the 19th and 20th centuries.', NULL, 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
