('481', 'CO', '011497', 'UG', 'Introduction to Quantum Information Processing', 'Basics of computational complexity; basics of quantum information; quantum phenomena; quantum circuits and universality; relationship between quantum and classical complexity classes; simple quantum algorithms; quantum Fourier transform; Shor factoring algorithm; Grover search algorithm; physical realization of quantum computation; error-correction and fault-tolerance; quantum key distribution. [Offered: F, W]', 'Prereq: One of MATH 114, 115, 235, 245; Level at least 4A', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
