('353', 'PSCI', '011637', 'UG', 'Politics in Russia', 'What explains the successes and failures of democratization in Russia? Students will undertake the comparative study of political processes, institutions, and reforms in Russia, focusing on the dilemmas posed by democratization and authoritarianism. [Note: One of PSCI 244, 250, 252, 255, 259, 260, 264 strongly recommended]', 'Prereq: Level at least 2B', 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
