('149', 'SPCOM', '015845', 'UG', 'Introduction to Critical Design Practices', 'How does design help us think? This studio course introduces students to practice-based methods for generating knowledge. Topics may include prototyping, performance as research, material thinking, multi-modal representation, and experience design. Students will test and explore how we learn differently through creative practices.', NULL, 'No Consent Required', 'No Consent Required', NULL),
